    <item>
      <title>Solaria 股价飙升，据称该公司正在吸引收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/spain-s-solaria-is-said-to-draw-takeover-offers-in-energy-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，由于投资者寻找该领域的便宜货，这家西班牙太阳能开发商收到了未经请求的收购建议，其股价因此创下八个月以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/spain-s-solaria-is-said-to-draw-takeover-offers-in-energy-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:05:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>历峰集团旗下奢侈品在线零售商 Net-A-Porter 将退出中国市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/richemont-s-online-luxury-retailer-net-a-porter-to-exit-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费支出疲软给中国这个全球第二大经济体的高端品牌运营带来越来越大的压力，历峰集团旗下的奢侈品电商平台 Yoox Net-A-Porter 决定退出中国市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/richemont-s-online-luxury-retailer-net-a-porter-to-exit-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:04:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Atos 获得法国 7 亿欧元收购战略部门的出价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/atos-gets-700-million-bid-from-france-for-strategic-businesses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为重组这家陷入困境的 IT 公司的讨论的一部分，法国政府提出以 7 亿欧元（7.51 亿美元）的企业价值收购 Atos SE 大数据和安全部门的一些业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/atos-gets-700-million-bid-from-france-for-strategic-businesses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 06:43:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
