    <item>
      <title>人工智能需求推动韩国芯片出口价格 5 月创纪录上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/ai-demand-helps-korean-chip-export-prices-to-record-jump-in-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[5 月份，韩国半导体出口价格以创纪录的速度上涨，凸显出人工智能推动韩国经济发展的强劲势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/ai-demand-helps-korean-chip-export-prices-to-record-jump-in-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 02:21:16 GMT</pubDate>
